  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "AWS Platform Lead",
  "description": "<p>Our client is seeking an AWS Platform Lead to manage the end-to-end onboarding of AWS accounts into a secure, compliant AWS Control Tower Landing Zone. This role bridges application, cloud, and security teams to ensure governance, security, and operational readiness before production handover.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><ul><li>Own AWS account onboarding from intake to production</li><li>Oversee account provisioning via <strong>AWS Control Tower</strong></li><li>Ensure security and compliance with <strong>CIS & AWS best practices</strong></li><li>Coordinate stakeholders and provide onboarding status updates</li><li>Drive automation and process improvements</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><ul><li>5+ years’ experience in AWS/cloud platform delivery or operations</li><li>Strong knowledge of AWS Control Tower, Organizations, IAM, networking, and security services</li><li>Experience with IaC tools (Terraform / CloudFormation)</li><li>Familiarity with CIS benchmarks and governance frameworks</li><li>Strong stakeholder management and communication skills</li><li>AWS certifications are a plus</li></ul><p><strong>To Apply</strong><br />To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p></p>",
